title: Showcase & Community Wins
body:
  - type: markdown
    attributes:
      value: |
        # ðŸŽ‰ Showcase & Community Wins

        Share your success stories, projects, and use cases with the {{ image.name }} community!
        
        This is a space to celebrate accomplishments and inspire others.

  - type: textarea
    id: project-title
    attributes:
      label: Project/Use Case Title
      description: What are you showcasing?
      placeholder: "Building a production-grade microservices platform with {{ image.name }}"
      validations:
        required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: project-description
    attributes:
      label: Project Description
      description: Tell us about your project and how you used {{ image.name }}
      placeholder: |
        ### Overview
        We built a containerized deployment platform that...

        ### Challenges Solved
        - [Challenge 1]
        - [Challenge 2]

        ### Results
        - Performance improvement: X%
        - Time saved: Y hours
        - Cost reduction: Z%
      validations:
        required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: technical-details
    attributes:
      label: Technical Stack
      description: What technologies and tools did you use with {{ image.name }}?
      placeholder: |
        - Docker version: 24.0
        - Kubernetes: v1.28
        - CI/CD: GitHub Actions
        - Registry: ghcr.io
      validations:
        required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: key-learnings
    attributes:
      label: Key Learnings & Tips
      description: What did you learn? What tips would you share with others?
      placeholder: |
        - Best practice 1: ...
        - Tip 2: ...
        - What we'd do differently: ...

  - type: textarea
    id: metrics
    attributes:
      label: Impact Metrics (if applicable)
      description: Share any metrics that demonstrate success
      placeholder: |
        - Build time reduced from 30m to 5m
        - Image size: 2.5GB â†’ 500MB
        - Deployment frequency: weekly â†’ daily

  - type: textarea
    id: resources
    attributes:
      label: Resources & Links
      description: Share relevant links (GitHub repo, blog post, documentation, etc.)
      placeholder: |
        - GitHub Repository: https://github.com/...
        - Blog Post: https://...
        - Live Demo: https://...

  - type: textarea
    id: contact-info
    attributes:
      label: Contact Information (Optional)
      description: If you'd like others to reach out, share how they can contact you
      placeholder: |
        - GitHub: @username
        - LinkedIn: https://linkedin.com/in/...
        - Email: [if comfortable sharing]

  - type: checkboxes
    id: permission
    attributes:
      label: Permissions
      description: Can we share this story with the community?
      options:
        - label: Yes, feel free to share this in announcements or documentation
        - label: Yes, you can feature this on the project website
        - label: Yes, include in monthly community highlights
